model.name: Kronik2008 - Improving alloreactive CTL immunotherapy for malignant gliomas using a simulation model of their interactive dynamics

body.pre: This mathematical model describes interactions between glioma tumors and the immune system that may occur following direct intra-tumoral administration of ex-vivo activated alloreactive cytotoxic-T-lymphocytes (aCTLs) as part of adoptive immunotherapy. The model includes descriptions of aCTL, neoplastic cells, MHC class I and II molecules, TGF-beta and IFN-gamma.
